{"word":"ἐξαναδύομαι","slug":"ἐξαναδύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξαναδύομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> with aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>ἐξανέδυν</el>\n<el>(aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>ἐξανέδυν</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> , <i>to rise out of, emerge from</i> water, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to escape from</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}